track.name: Tutu
comments: Oh, the best jazz song, ya?

AuAu, BuBu, CuCu, Du Du, EuEu, FuFu, GuGu, HuHu, IuIu, JuJu, KuKu, LuLu, MuMu, NuNu, OuOu, PuPu, QuQu, RuRu, SuSu and now TuTu. 
Suppose the next ones will be UuUu, VuVu, WuWu, XuXu and ZuZu.
Voodoo with a touch of Digeridoo and, of course, the blues. Miles ahead.
esa es la forma de hacer JAZZ.................
live around the world: best version
Sax solo live at MTV Jazz is so incredible! God, I can listen to this all the time!! :):)
I agree completely with you, MusicMagic7!
Great live version but i prefer the lp version

I agree with andyhusmith; sketches from siesta is just one of the greatest works miles has ever done!
still, tutu is great!

simmek: oh yeah, really. I mean, this gets so old.. like when there's a video about a pretty woman and ppl say in the comments "lol she's my neighbour".
so yeah, sure you met him..

ajo, yesterday, i saw him at the railwaystation, he asked me to light his cigarette and suddenly we began to play tutu for marcus miller who asked me to join him at a shopping-trip^^
he had to go because his wife wanted him to come home and wash the dishes....
AuAu, BuBu, CuCu, Du Du, EuEu, FuFu, GuGu, HuHu, IuIu, JuJu, KuKu, LuLu, MuMu, NuNu, OuOu, PuPu, QuQu, RuRu, SuSu and now TuTu. Suppose the next ones will be UuUu, VuVu, WuWu, XuXu and ZuZu.
today they would call it "nu-jazz", and somehow they would be right, finally.
